{
  "stem": "27340.3",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 11.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And it took us a long time to try and persuade them that, yes, unfortunately, we were born in Germany, but nevertheless we were Jewish and we were victims of their persecution and we were just as much interested in winning this war as they were, because it was our war just as much it was theirs.",
      "word_count": 57
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "The only difference was that they were grown-up men and they were digging for victory in the coal mines, and we were still kids and couldn't, in fact, serve in any specific way, either in the forces or even in the coal mines.",
      "word_count": 43
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, very much so, yes.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "By that time, the villagers had begun to realize, you know, about six months after we'd arrive there originally, what in fact our status really was.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, yes, of course.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Because the area was on the outer perimeter of the Birmingham, which as you know was a major manufacturing center, the major city, there were a number of anti-aircraft batteries around there.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And during air raids on Birmingham, then quite clearly we were forced to go into shelters in the same way as everybody else.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Yes, of course we witnessed the war, as civilians did and in those sort of areas.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We were, of course, very keenly interested in the progress of how the war was going.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And in those early days, the war was not going too well, as far as we were concerned.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Germany was invading more and more countries.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And the situation was looking grimmer and grimmer all the time.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I did, yes, because my parents were in England.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And my father was interned on the Isle of Man as an enemy alien.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "He was, after all, of German nationality.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
